attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate - All Seasons
Alexandria Brokers Realty dba ABR Realty

data.description:
Discover a 5-acre country haven just 10 mins from town, offering panoramic views, sunsets, and income from rentable land. The 4-bed, 2-bath farmhouse (approx. 2180 sq ft) seamlessly blends comfort and style. The kitchen, with stainless steel appliances and custom cabinets, anchors the home. Outside, enjoy a wrap-around custom paver patio and a new vinyl fence.
Oversized buildings include an insulated/heated barn, ideal for small businesses, contractors, or farmers. Oversized garage doors cater to large equipment, with in-floor heating in half the barn for vehicles, equipment, or toys. The barn is fully spray foamed and features a freshly built office upstairs. An additional 3-stall detached garage offers ample storage.
Immerse in country living with modern comforts and amazing out buildings. This residence is a rare opportunity to own a slice of countryside paradise that features serene ambiance, sunsets, and endless possibilities! Homeowners have ~ a 6.7% assumable loan.
